:: Notes on possible memory limit implementation.
-> ./mm/mmap.c:
mmap_region: main function for doing mmap.
may_expand_vm: checks for memlimit, uses struct rlimit. 
-> ./kernel/sys.c:
do_prlimit: allows to change struct rlimit.

Plan: update rlimit each time task asks may_expand_vm.
new_lim = overall_limit - cur_lim.

:: Notes on possible threading implementation.
./kernel/fork.c:
do_fork: core function for all forks/clones/vforks.
....:
wake_up_new_task: called by do_fork.

Plan: hook something of above.
